NMR Documentation


This is the documentation for the nmr module.


#


nmr
 
 
Module
.


nmr - Naive MapReduce module


NMR is a Naive MapReduce implementation. It has a simple interface that allows the user to input a filename and process it in a map-reduce fashion.
